Package org.bluezoo.gumdrop.ldap.asn1

Class ASN1Type

java.lang.Object
org.bluezoo.gumdrop.ldap.asn1.ASN1Type
public final class ASN1Type extends Object
ASN.1 type constants and tag manipulation utilities.

ASN.1 tags are encoded as follows:

 Bits 7-6: Class
   00 = Universal
   01 = Application
   10 = Context-specific
   11 = Private

 Bit 5: Primitive/Constructed
   0 = Primitive
   1 = Constructed

 Bits 4-0: Tag number (0-30, or 31 for multi-byte tag)
Author:
Chris Burdess
